    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Thin silver coins issued by Constantine in the 320s, used until the late 4th century, and reintroduced during the Byzantine period between about 700 and the early 11th century.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Monedas de plata delgadas emitidas por Constantino en los ñoas 320, usadas hasta el siglo IV tardío y reintroducidas durante el período bizantino entre aproximadamente el 700 y el siglo XI temprano.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Dunne zilveren munten uitgegeven door Constantijn in ¦320 en gebruikt tot eind 4e eeuw; tijdens de Byzantijnse periode vanaf ¦700 tot het begin van de 11e eeuw werden ze opnieuw geslagen.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>君士坦丁大帝於西元320年代發行之薄銀幣，使用至西元四世紀晚期。於西元七世紀至十一世紀早期的拜占庭時期，再度為世人使用。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
